modelVersions.name: KlokGen Ethical v1.1
modelVersions.description:
This is a directly improved model over v1 of KlokGen Ethical. This model is capable, as before, of creating halfbodies and quarterbodies.

However, v1.1 introduces the ability to specify FE9-Style for your halfbodies, as well as FE10-Style. Currently, FE10-Style looks a little fucky, but that will be fixed later when I upload the FE10-Specific model, as well as the Halfbody-Only model.

Additionally, you can use Tellius-Style to create a mixed style of FE9 and FE10, as shown in the example images.

Quarterbodies and the dataset in general has been improved a bit. Remember, if you use a keyword like "Ike \(Fire Emblem\)", you will be able to gen based on that character's general appearance. If that character has a specific Danbooru tag, their data may also be added from Danbooru and this Lora combined. Lyn, is a good example, as she is a popular character on Danbooru.

For those popular character, use their specific game name. "Lyn \(Fire Emblem: Blazing Blade\)" will have better results than "Lyn \(Fire Emblem\)".

I will be posting single-style and dual-style Loras over the next few hours. They will be even better at replicating their specific styles than this unified Lora!

This model works best with Macross Ultimate. Run the Lora at 0.8 strength.

modelVersions.name: KlokGen Quarterbodies ONLY v1.1
modelVersions.description:
This model is for Quarterbodies only. These are the most finicky type of FE gens, and as such, they require specific settings to look good. My team is struggling to improve them, but our preferred settings are:

Use the Macross Ultimate model from this page.
DPM++ SDE at 15 Steps, 512x512, CFG 4
If you have Umi AI installed, you can use these negatives to improve the art style:

lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry, out of focus, censorship, (multiple boys, multiple characters, multiple girls, multiple views:1.2), boobplate, NEGS Bad Artist Anime by nick-x-hacker, NEGS Bad Artist OG by nick-x-hacker, NEGS Easy Negative

And finally, this is a good starting prompt to try out:
solo focus, (quarterbody, frames, vanilla fire emblem:1.1), simple background, {caucasian|dark skin|colored skin}, {1boy, mature male|1 boy, teenage boy, aged down|1girl, mature woman, large breasts|1girl, teenage girl, aged down}, {<[military]>, <[heavy armor|heavy armor]>|<[Torso]>}, <[hair color]>, <[hair length]>

Remember to run this Lora at 0.8 strength with the Macross Ultimate model for the best results!

Update dataset and upload lycoris version. Adjust trigger tag to soyincapazz, username of this artist. The preview images of the new model are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled with 'SD Upscale'.

2023/4/1 upate

Fix the compatibility problem of non-NAI-based checkpoints. Now arbitrary anime model with NAI's VAE or kl-f8-anime2 VAE can also generate good results using this LoRA, theoretically.

2023/3/1 update

Reduce loss to 0.09. 0.6 and 0.7 weight should be enough.

Introduction

A LORA model of Tsuki no i-min style. The 784MB VAEs are recommended. 0.6~0.8 weights are good.

Cautions (Must Read)

  • Some preview images are generated using hires fix. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

  • The maximum of generating resolution should not exceed 1024 theoretically, otherwise extra/deformed head/limbs will be waiting for you :). Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.description:
This has more image to train, so it looks much better.

More preview on my Pixiv: 4BEraser - pixiv

I use Colab to run it, so it didn't finish and stopped on epoch13.

How to use:

You can input nothing to generate the character any way, but I do recommend you to use following prompts to generate the outfit:

  • Base: Graf Zeppelin /(Kancolle/), grey eyes, (large breasts:1.3)

  • Outfit: black gloves, black pantyhose, sidelocks, peaked cap, pleated skirt, black skirt, necktie, miniskirt, military uniform, iron cross, white capelet, long sleeves, white headwear, military hat, white jacket,

  • Try other tags by your own, this has a wide variety of possible clothings, since this model is bit overfitted, don't forget to put those official outfit element into negative prompts, and lower the model weight. I have updated some examples for reference.

    • NSFW compatible.

    • I'm not a fan of realistic model, but it seems being capable with ChilloutMix.

    • If you find out that it's focusing on chara's feet, you can try to use Controlnet to limit it.

Settings are what I am using, you can change by your own.

  • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

  • about 20 steps, CFG scale 5~7

  • LoRA Weight: maybe above 0.6, try it by your own

  • If using highres

    • ESRGAN_4X

    • Denoising 0.4-0.6.

LoRA Train Info

  • based on Animefull-pruned

    • 8x low quality 48 images

    • 16x medium quality 51 images

    • 32x high quality 33 images

    • => 1 epoch = 1128 images

items.description:
If you like my LoRAs please consider to support me by buying me a coffee here so I can make a new LoRA faster. I do open commissions there too if you want to make your own custom LoRA.

Trigger word: fromisjiheon

Use CLIP SKIP 2. You may need to use HIRES FIX with denoise strength between 0.5-0.7, Hires steps 20-30 is good but you can use whatever you want. Upscaler use 4x Foolhardy Remacri or SWINIR 4x.

Best checkpoints/models to use:

Realistic: VisionGen, ChillOutMix, ArtEros, Snapdd00, Henrealmix

Fanart/painting style: Dreamshaper, LucidMix, SunshineMix, Majicmix

Use it wisely. I don't responsible for anything you generated with this LoRa.

items.name: Miyamoto Rei (HOTD) - Character
items.description:
LoRA trained with images of character Miyamoto Rei (High School of the Dead)

v1.5 (NEW)

Increased dataset, modified tags, cleaned up tags, used new and improved training parameters. This results in a both more consistent and flexible LoRA. It works with more models and can be combined with other LoRAs. The example images combine with another character LoRA.

Additional info

I make these models for fun and for the challenge and release them for free for everyone to enjoy, for non-commercial use (see license). The one thing I ask of you is to provide rating and feedback! That helps me understand where I can improve and helps me stay motivated to produce more content!

I accept suggestions or requests here or on Civitai discord server.

You can also check my more polished images and upcoming models on my pixiv profile.

-- previous versions --

v1.5

New training parameters, tags and dataset. Trained on NAI. Tested on AOM2, Perfect World, NeverEnding Dream, and other models. Works with 1.0 weight and 0.3-0.7 CFG, but depends on the model.

You don't need a trigger word to get the character. For the basic uniform you can simply use the trigger "serafuku". You can also add to the positive or negative prompt to get variations from the tagged training data: shirt, skirt, thighhighs, elbow pads, knee pads, sneakers, rifle, stick, blood, torn clothes, shoulder holster.

See the information in the image examples, including for tested models.

Works with multiple models and LoRAs.

v1.0

Better results with 0.5-0.7 weight and 0.3-0.6 CFG (v1.0), but it may depend on the model used.

Works with realistic and anime models and to work with other characters and styles (see examples on how to achieve this). Clothes can be changed by adding, removing or reordering these tags:

"green sailor collar, black bow, green skirt, black thighhighs, long sleeves, brown hair, brown eyes, hair between eyes, ponytail, sneakers, white footwear"

(tip: don't describe the shoes if you don't want a full body image)

See the version information for more on the LoRA training. Please post your images and let me know your feedback.

items.name: Hishi Amazon (umamusume)
items.description:
LoRA of Hishi Amazon (umamusume)

Old racing clothes is so hot 👍

All of my works is free. If you'd like to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. 👍

Recommend options

  • LoRA weight 0.7~1.0

  • Trigger words

    • base

      • hishi amazon \(umamusume\)

    • Racing competition clothes :

      • crop top, bandeau, white choker, single sleeves, arm ribbon, pleated skirt, thigh strap, white skirt, miniskirt, bikini skirt, layered skirt, thigh strap, leg ribbon, blue footwear

      • (optional) hand on hip, hand on own thigh, leaning forward

    • Old racing competition clothes :

      • sailor collar, wide sleeves, blue neckerchief, white shirt, sailor dress, thigh strap, blue footwear, tanlines, bikini tan, off shoulder, cleavage, bare shoulders

      • (optional) bikini under clothes, blue skirt

    • Casual clothes :

      • red shirt, fang, torn clothes, choker, bracelet, jewelry, long sleeves, bare shoulders, midriff, torn jeans, torn pants, denim, red footwear, shoes, sneakers

    • Tracen school uniform :

      • white thighhighs, tracen school uniform, purple shirt, pleated skirt, puffy short sleeves, white skirt, puffy sleeves, summer uniform, frilled skirt, sailor collar, sailor shirt, miniskirt, frills

Use animefull based model

  • Settings

    • Stable Diffusion WebUI by Automatic1111

    • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

    • about 20 steps, CFG scale 3.5~6.5

    • kl-f8-anime2.vae

    • CLIP skip = 1

    • Use highres. fix to get higher quality image

      • Upscaler : Latent series

      • Denoising strength 0.50~0.65

LoRA training info

  • trained on sd-scripts by kohya_ss. Thank you a lot!

  • based on Animefull-pruned

  • 115 images of taiki shuttle

    • 4x low quality 39 images

    • 8x medium quality 32 images

    • 16x high quality 44 images

    • => 1 epoch = 1116 images

  • replaced character feature tags with hishi amazon \(umamusume\)

    • horse girl, horse tail, purple hair, orange eyes, etc.

  • resolution : 768x768

  • rank=alpha=16

  • batch size = 4, 7 epochs trained

  • other training settings included in training_data.zip

This LoRA may be compatible with animefull-based models (ex. AbyssOrangeMix Series...)

All uploaded images are generated by AOM3A1

items.name: Pokimane [Reupload]
items.description:
Award-winning Twitch streamer and YouTuber Pokimane, now available for Stable Diffusion through textual inversion!

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. The training set included a few images of her with curly hair as well, so adding 'curly hair' to your prompt should easily change her hairstyle. Any limits you might encounter with the embedding can be countered by using inpainting or lowering the weight in your prompts.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
